4. Emit cfactor_regression signal if C-Factor regression detected
5. Run TierProgression.analyze() on batch (insights/heuristics)
6. Replay heuristics back into analysis
7. Cluster episodes by (plan_id, task_type, outcome, model)
8. For each cluster:
